a us marine corps a4 jet fighter 
crashed on brewer mountain about 20 miles northwest of heber 
springs on monday but the pilot ejected and was uninjured an air 
force spokesman said 
the plane assigned to marine air group 42 detachment b at 
memphis naval air station in tennessee was involved in local 
