here at a glance are main provisions of the 
12 billion anticrime package president bush proposed monday 
bush would 
make permanent a ban on imported semiautomatic assault rifles 
if the bureau of alcohol tobacco and firearms rules they are not 
for sport but allow us manufacturers to keep making and selling 
such weapons 
ban semiautomatic ammunition clips of more than 15 rounds 
double the current fiveyear minimum sentence for using a 
