block the practice of dropping many gunuse charges through 
plea bargaining 
spend 1 billion for new prison construction identify 
government properties and facilities for conversion to jails and 
prisons 
execute people who commit such federal offenses as murder for 
hire killings by federal prisoners serving life sentences 
terrorist murders of american citizens and murders of hostages 
also allow executions for such crimes as treason and espionage 
under provisions now in disuse because statutes do not satisfy 
supreme court guidelines 
