the skirmishing erupted monday after the president unveiled 
plans for a permanent ban on imports of many semiautomatic assault 
weapons and a ban on the manufacture of ammunition magazines for 
those guns containing more than 15 rounds 
the proposal is part of a 12 billion anticrime package that 
also calls for building new prisons hiring more federal agents 
widening the death penalty and toughening sentences for illegally 
using semiautomatic guns 
