world war ii massacre of polish officers including his father at 
katyn in the soviet union the government has been edging toward 
acknowledging soviet guilt for the massacre 
in a province where a committee actively seeks the fate of some 
200 residents rounded up by the soviet secret police in 1945 and 
believed executed the allusion to katyn was vivid 
id vote for him 19yearold bartosz iwanowski said 
support for wajda and geremek is quite big when people see 
these names they immediately just sign underneath even party 
members sign our list for wajda said grzegorz wilczynski 
