the paytelevision programmer home box office 
inc said today it plans to launch the first advertisersupported 
channel devoted entirely to comedy starting this fall 
the new service which would be offered to cable operators for 
inclusion at no extra charge to subscribers to their basic service 
would represent the time inc units first venture into basic cable 
programming 
