several other recently launched cable networks among the newcomers 
are turner broadcasting system incs turner network television 
the national broadcasting cos consumer news and business channel 
and an array of regional sports networks 
michael fuchs home box office chairman and chief executive 
said in a news release disclosing the plans that his company has 
presented the concept of a comedy network to cable operators across 
the country over the past several months and that the idea has 
received strong support 
we anticipate demographics that will attract strong advertiser 
attention consistent programming that will score well with 
consumers and a new basic service that will generate a healthy cash 
flow for the cable operator he said 
